1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:41,009
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,670 --> 00:01:43,950
[Episode 9]

4
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:45,870
Hasn't your daughter-in-law, Chuntiao,

5
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:46,700
come back?

6
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,150
She?

7
00:01:49,229 --> 00:01:50,550
After my son died,

8
00:01:51,789 --> 00:01:54,070
she became even crazier.

9
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,190
What...

10
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,570
What does that mean?

11
00:01:57,800 --> 00:02:00,740
She despised my son for being a coroner.

12
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,090
They quarreled every day,

13
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:05,710
and she often ran away.

14
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:14,260
Coroners are not government officers.

15
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:16,070
They are neither officials

16
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:17,030
nor clerks.

17
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:19,070
They are only called upon

18
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,590
when there is a murder case.

19
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:23,670
The payment for postmortem is pitifully low.

20
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,520
Since they often deal with corpses,

21
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:29,430
people think karma will find them,

22
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:30,079
and thus,

23
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:32,110
they are not respected.

24
00:02:32,230 --> 00:02:32,829
However,

25
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:35,590
a coroner is indispensable

26
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:37,230
and irreplaceable

27
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:38,990
in solving cases.

28
00:02:39,270 --> 00:02:41,110
Determining the time of death,

29
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,990
reconstructing the method of the crime,

30
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:45,110
and finding the murder weapon

31
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,840
all rely on the coroner.

32
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:51,470
It is truly a humble position with heavy responsibilities.

33
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,390
You...

34
00:02:55,510 --> 00:02:58,110
actually understand coroners so well.

35
00:03:01,270 --> 00:03:02,350
Many people

36
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:06,270
are unwilling to live next to a coroner.

37
00:03:06,290 --> 00:03:07,210
In many places,

38
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:09,480
they even require coroners

39
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:12,190
to use doors made of black wood

40
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:14,270
to distinguish them from others.

41
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,530
Just now, when I came in, I noticed it.

42
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,110
It looks like Shiyang

43
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:21,120
also has this custom.

44
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:24,240
People from a coroner's family

45
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:26,190
cannot participate in the imperial examinations.

46
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,280
If it's a girl,

47
00:03:27,590 --> 00:03:30,990
it's not easy to find a good marriage.

48
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:37,190
You understand the hardships

49
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:41,390
of a coroner's family so well.

50
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:45,150
Madam,

51
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:49,190
today, it was my honor to assist you in the postmortem.

52
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:52,150
Your precise technique and accurate judgment

53
00:03:52,390 --> 00:03:54,790
have truly impressed me.

54
00:03:54,950 --> 00:03:56,990
After hearing what you said,

55
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:01,430
I'm no longer afraid of losing face.

56
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,560
Although Chuntiao is good,

57
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:05,830
I'm afraid

58
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,770
she can't escape involvement

59
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:11,190
in my son's death.

60
00:04:16,709 --> 00:04:18,269
She has a younger brother

61
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,470
named Chunshan.

62
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,420
Half a month ago...

63
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:26,970
[Treasure Pavilion]

64
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:29,530
Dong Haogu,

65
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:30,670
I'm warning you!

66
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:31,910
If you dare to seduce my sister ever again,

67
00:04:31,910 --> 00:04:33,110
I won't go easy on you!

68
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,230
She's here for tea.

69
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:38,000
How could you say I seduced her?

70
00:04:39,030 --> 00:04:40,390
There's no smoke without fire!

71
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,750
You don't have to admit it.

72
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,680
But I, Chunshan,

73
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,490
am upright!

74
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:45,430
And my brother-in-law treats me well.

75
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:46,330
Even the shoes on my feet

76
00:04:46,330 --> 00:04:47,330
were given by him.

77
00:04:48,110 --> 00:04:49,390
Consider this a warning today.

78
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,470
If it happens again,

79
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:51,310
I'll kill you!

80
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:55,090
Can this be considered speaking out of righteousness?

81
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:57,870
You came to tell me about it,

82
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:01,060
aren't you afraid that my son will kill your sister?

83
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:04,520
[Chunshan, Dugu Yang's brother-in-law]

84
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:02,330
Well...

85
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:04,160
She deserves it.

86
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:06,830
I, Chunshan, am a man of integrity

87
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:08,550
and can't stand such things.

88
00:05:08,550 --> 00:05:09,610
If this continues,

89
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:10,610
it won't be my sister

90
00:05:10,610 --> 00:05:11,670
being killed by my brother-in-law,

91
00:05:11,670 --> 00:05:12,330
but my brother-in-law

92
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:13,530
being killed by them.

93
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,110
Fine.

94
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:18,150
How much money

95
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:20,600
do you want

96
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,510
from me today?

97
00:05:25,370 --> 00:05:27,330
Chunshan is a ne'er-do-well.

98
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:29,500
I suspect

99
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:32,210
that on that day,

100
00:05:32,350 --> 00:05:34,590
he actually went to extort Dong Haogu,

101
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,950
and only turned against him because he didn't get the money.

102
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:40,880
However, the affair between Dong Haogu and Chuntiao

103
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:43,350
may not be entirely false.

104
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,990
After Dugu Yang found out,

105
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:47,230
what did he say?

106
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,670
My son is honest.

107
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:53,830
He didn't say anything.

108
00:05:58,260 --> 00:05:59,830
Is Chuntiao back?

109
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:01,950
No.

110
00:06:02,940 --> 00:06:04,030
It sounds

111
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:06,070
like a thief.

112
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,350
A thief?

113
00:06:10,950 --> 00:06:11,470
Mr. Su.

114
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:12,840
Let me do it.

115
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,110
How dare you!

116
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,060
Stop!

117
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,790
If this thief is dead,

118
00:06:57,030 --> 00:06:58,750
there's no need for an autopsy.

119
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,880
He died from bleeding inside the skull

120
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:03,550
caused by a heavy blow to the back of the head.

121
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:07,830
Madam, don't worry.

122
00:07:08,590 --> 00:07:09,390
He won't die.

123
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,350
Who ambushed me?

124
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:14,150
It hurts so much.

125
00:07:16,910 --> 00:07:18,230
Chunshan, how dare you?

126
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:19,630
What did you go to Dugu Yang's house

127
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,350
to steal?

128
00:07:21,230 --> 00:07:21,790
Steal?

129
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,830
Dugu Yang was my brother-in-law.

130
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,510
The shoes on my feet were given by him.

131
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:27,150
I went to my brother-in-law's house today

132
00:07:27,150 --> 00:07:28,880
just to take some more clothes.

133
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,550
Was that stealing?

134
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,790
My brother-in-law has already died.

135
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,100
Except for me,

136
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,750
who else can his clothes be left to?

137
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:37,310
You know Dugu Yang has died?

138
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:40,490
You're the one who killed him, aren't you?

139
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,810
What are you talking about?

140
00:07:41,810 --> 00:07:43,830
I, Chunshan,

141
00:07:44,030 --> 00:07:45,760
am a man of integrity and pride.

142
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:48,159
Don't think just because you're high up there

143
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:50,360
that you can slander others as you wish.

144
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,600
So it's a misunderstanding.

145
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:56,830
You can leave now.

146
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:04,830
I can leave?

147
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:06,110
Goodbye.

148
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:07,790
Wait.

149
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,990
Is this yours?

150
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:14,550
Yes!

151
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,390
No!

152
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:18,550
It's not mine.

153
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:23,990
Guards.

154
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,490
Search him.

155
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:42,720
This is a burial goods store.

156
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,670
This clay figurine is for deterring tomb robbers.

157
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:45,800
You are so careless.

158
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:47,590
How did you solve the previous cases?

159
00:08:47,590 --> 00:08:48,550
I...

160
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,680
Chunshan.

161
00:09:03,990 --> 00:09:05,600
This dice

162
00:09:06,190 --> 00:09:07,070
was found

163
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:09,670
at the scene where Dugu Yang was killed.

164
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,810
Put him to torture.

165
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:19,930
No, no, no!

166
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:21,220
Don't torture me! Don't torture me!

167
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:22,110
I'll confess.

168
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:23,850
I'll confess everything.

169
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:30,950
Big or Small?

170
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,660
Big! Big! Big!

171
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,830
Small! Small!

172
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:34,350
Small!

173
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:34,710
Big!

174
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:35,740
Dice are out.

175
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:36,470
Small!

176
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:37,110
Big!

177
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:37,950
Small!

178
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,180
Chunshan,

179
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,920
the gambling tools this time

180
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,550
were brought by you yourself.

181
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,810
Are you convinced now?

182
00:09:58,830 --> 00:10:00,390
Could it be that I'll never turn my luck around

183
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,790
in this lifetime?

184
00:10:10,190 --> 00:10:11,230
Dong?

185
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:14,630
If you want to turn your luck around,

186
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,180
come to Treasure Pavilion.

187
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:18,710
Forget it.

188
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:20,450
Dong Haogu,

189
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,740
I've never gotten involved in the affair

190
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:23,140
between you and my sister.

191
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,600
I'm a bit tight on cash now.

192
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:25,880
Could you lend me some money?

193
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,880
Never?

194
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,670
Then who came to extort me last time?

195
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:31,430
How could that be extortion?

196
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:33,070
I, Chunshan, am righteous.

197
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:35,070
Last time, I was just reminding you.

198
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,670
Are you lending me money or not?

199
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:37,590
Making money

200
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,940
is better than borrowing.

201
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:42,380
Making money?

202
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,490
If I knew how to make money,

203
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:48,430
I would have gotten an umbrella like yours.

204
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:49,590
Help me find a thing.

205
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,150
Once I get it,

206
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:53,790
I'll pay you this amount.

207
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:55,840
Three thousand?

208
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:59,160
Look at your ambition.

209
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:02,120
Well,

210
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,750
even if it's just finding a lump of dirt,

211
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,610
it'll still take time and effort.

212
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:08,030
Three hundred...

213
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,000
Isn't it a bit too little?

214
00:11:13,170 --> 00:11:13,750
Okay!

215
00:11:14,170 --> 00:11:15,310
I can accept 300 mace.

216
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:17,240
Tell me, what do you need me to find?

217
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,740
I'm talking about thirty thousand mace.

218
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:22,350
Thirty thousand?

219
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:24,990
What do you want to find?

220
00:11:30,130 --> 00:11:31,490
Dugu Xin?

221
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,840
[Justice]

222
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:34,620
Multifaceted Seal?

223
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,070
Yes.

224
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:36,620
Dong Haogu said

225
00:11:36,990 --> 00:11:37,990
it's a treasure.

226
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,270
I was thinking

227
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:41,980
Dugu Yang definitely

228
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:42,910
didn't keep the treasure

229
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:43,750
at home.

230
00:11:44,310 --> 00:11:46,230
Otherwise, my sister would have known long ago

231
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,360
and wouldn't have had such a hard life.

232
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:50,680
Since it was not at home,

233
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:52,120
it must be at the burial goods store.

234
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,670
But Dugu Yang

235
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,830
was at the burial goods store every day,

236
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:56,560
working on those clay figurines until midnight.

237
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:58,260
I followed him for several days,

238
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,220
and finally,

239
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,840
I found an opportunity.

240
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:04,430
Coroner Dugu has a beautiful wife,

241
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:07,870
yet she was taken advantage of by others.

242
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,110
Bad boys!

243
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:11,850
Get lost!

244
00:12:12,390 --> 00:12:15,190
The new magistrate's surname is also Dugu.

245
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:16,550
You know what?

246
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,530
He invited me for drinks tonight.

247
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:21,430
He said the magistrate invited him for drinks.

248
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,800
As soon as I heard that, I knew it was just boasting.

249
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:27,140
No need to record this.

250
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:28,430
It must be recorded.

251
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:34,470
Chunshan,

252
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,500
keep going.

253
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:05,720
My goodness.

254
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,510
He's been dealing with these every day.

255
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:08,440
They scared me.

256
00:13:08,610 --> 00:13:10,750
Those clay figurines my brother-in-law made

257
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,950
all have mechanisms.

258
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,650
I dared not touch them.

259
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:16,890
So I searched inside and outside every room.

260
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,350
I searched for an hour

261
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,930
and still couldn't find it.

262
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:21,030
So I thought,

263
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,670
I might as well wait for him to return and tell him directly

264
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:26,150
that if he has the treasure, he should bring it out,

265
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,260
and I'll go and find Dong Haogu on his behalf,

266
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:29,400
get a good price,

267
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,440
and take a share.

268
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:31,660
So,

269
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,960
I sat on the chair waiting for him.

270
00:14:03,190 --> 00:14:04,520
That's the whole story.

271
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:05,680
So I left the dice

272
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,730
at the burial goods store.

273
00:14:07,780 --> 00:14:09,100
I went out of town yesterday

274
00:14:09,100 --> 00:14:10,030
to meet a friend.

275
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,160
When I returned,

276
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:13,670
I heard that Dugu Yang had died.

277
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,590
I cried so hard.

278
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:19,070
Since I was young,

279
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:20,270
my brother-in-law

280
00:14:20,270 --> 00:14:21,550
has been the best person to me.

281
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:22,240
I told you

282
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:23,540
I wasn't stealing.

283
00:14:23,540 --> 00:14:25,740
I just wanted to keep some of his clothes

284
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:27,080
as a memento.

285
00:14:27,900 --> 00:14:29,080
Yang!

286
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:31,550
How could you pass away like this?

287
00:14:32,370 --> 00:14:34,890
Who will take care of me in the future?

288
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:36,910
Enough. Stop crying.

289
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,230
What you said

290
