617
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:52,410
[Shiyang]

618
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:00,600
Magistrate,

619
00:29:00,670 --> 00:29:02,330
Dong Haogu has been arrested.

620
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:04,910
Let him wait.

621
00:29:07,020 --> 00:29:07,750
Let him wait!

622
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:08,390
Yes.

623
