You're not a suspect.

630
00:29:49,910 --> 00:29:51,910
There's no need for interrogation.

631
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:52,730
Have a seat.

632
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,520
Are you going to ask about Dong Haogu

