638
00:30:16,320 --> 00:30:17,360
The first person I thought of

639
00:30:16,610 --> 00:30:18,560
[Treasure Pavilion]

640
00:30:17,390 --> 00:30:18,390
was Dong Haogu.

641
00:30:22,530 --> 00:30:23,330
Have some tea.

642
00:30:23,990 --> 00:30:25,190
The death of Dugu Yang

643
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,720
