747
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:04,710
Get lost!

748
00:34:14,889 --> 00:34:16,750
I, Chuntiao, have been reckless,

749
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:18,460
but I am innocent.

750
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:21,070
I went out to have tea

751
00:34:21,270 --> 00:34:22,300
