761
00:34:52,949 --> 00:34:53,550
Chuntiao.

762
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:54,949
Tell me.

763
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,949
Is Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal

764
00:34:56,949 --> 00:34:58,270
in your possession?

765
00:34:59,350 --> 00:35:00,150
No.

766
00:35:00,790 --> 00:35:01,470
I have never seen

767
00:35:01,470 --> 00:35:02,990
that multifaceted seal.

