830
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:42,790
I don't want to bear your children.

831
00:37:55,830 --> 00:37:57,630
I was just speaking out of anger.

832
00:37:59,870 --> 00:38:01,470
I wanted him to sell that seal

833
00:38:02,110 --> 00:38:03,640
