862
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,060
It was because I learned

863
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:21,060
Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal is here.

864
00:39:21,210 --> 00:39:21,910
Initially,

865
00:39:21,950 --> 00:39:23,470
