870
00:39:30,610 --> 00:39:32,020
a poor coroner.

871
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,430
When exactly

872
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:38,590
did you go to the burial goods store?

873
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:44,310
I left home at 9:45 p.m.

874
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:50,900
[Lingdu Burial Goods Store]

875
00:39:56,250 --> 00:39:58,380
Aren't you going to ask me why I'm here?

876
00:39:58,830 --> 00:40:00,070
What else could it be,

877
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:03,320
besides the seal?

878
00:40:04,710 --> 00:40:05,430
Smart man.

879
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:08,040
In fact, besides Chuntiao,

880
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:08,840
I also asked

881
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:10,380
your unreliable brother-in-law,

882
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:11,060
Chunshan.

883
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,620
But I thought about it,

884
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:15,320
why don't we talk face to face?

885
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:18,120
So I came here in the rain.

886
00:40:18,430 --> 00:40:19,290
I didn't expect

887
00:40:19,900 --> 00:40:21,560
you'd actually be in the shop.

888
00:40:23,630 --> 00:40:25,130
Let's get straight to the point.

889
00:40:25,130 --> 00:40:26,950
I'll pay you 150 thousand mace.

890
00:40:27,830 --> 00:40:29,510
Sell me Dugu Xin

891
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:30,650
Multifaceted Seal.

892
00:40:30,750 --> 00:40:32,270
No.

893
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:34,920
It's a waste

894
00:40:34,950 --> 00:40:36,680
in your hands anyway, isn't it?

895
00:40:41,910 --> 00:40:42,550
Dugu Yang,

896
00:40:43,270 --> 00:40:45,400
is that seal really a family heirloom?

897
00:40:46,610 --> 00:40:48,740
Who would believe you're a descendant

898
00:40:49,270 --> 00:40:50,630
of Dugu Xin?

899
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:03,700
Fine.

900
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:05,560
I was convinced.

901
00:41:05,990 --> 00:41:07,720
I'll pay you 180 thousand mace.

902
00:41:12,750 --> 00:41:13,870
Take a look

903
00:41:13,870 --> 00:41:15,400
at where your mother lives.

904
00:41:15,630 --> 00:41:16,790
You finally got a wife,

905
00:41:16,790 --> 00:41:18,790
but she always goes out with others.

906
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:20,230
Look at you.

907
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:22,800
Keeping the treasure seal is useless for you.

908
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:24,550
It's better to exchange it for some money

909
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:26,010
and turn your luck around.

910
00:41:26,060 --> 00:41:27,410
Your ancestors in heaven

911
00:41:27,410 --> 00:41:28,670
would also be pleased.

912
00:41:31,950 --> 00:41:33,610
Are you really not selling it?

913
00:41:34,740 --> 00:41:36,750
Your head must be made of mud.

914
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:38,990
200 thousand.

915
00:41:39,950 --> 00:41:40,950
300 thousand.

916
00:41:44,270 --> 00:41:45,800
Do you really have the seal?

917
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:47,410
This is how much I want,

918
00:41:47,790 --> 00:41:49,470
not a penny less.

919
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:54,910
230 thousand.

920
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:00,350
240 thousand.

921
00:42:02,710 --> 00:42:03,250
Dugu Yang,

922
00:42:03,250 --> 00:42:04,720
300 thousand is impossible.

923
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:05,470
250 thousand!

924
00:42:05,470 --> 00:42:06,190
Deal!

925
00:42:08,590 --> 00:42:09,720
I've figured it out.

926
00:42:12,310 --> 00:42:13,630
I do need money.

927
00:42:15,790 --> 00:42:17,520
Here's what you're going to do:

928
00:42:17,710 --> 00:42:19,410
convert all the money into silver ingots.

929
00:42:19,410 --> 00:42:20,870
Bring it to me

930
00:42:20,870 --> 00:42:22,020
by 1 o'clock tonight.

931
00:42:22,020 --> 00:42:23,150
You want it tonight?

932
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,810
Forget it if you have no money.

933
00:42:25,070 --> 00:42:25,950
No! Wait!

934
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:26,950
I'll get it.

935
00:42:30,390 --> 00:42:31,460
I gathered all the silver ingots

936
00:42:31,460 --> 00:42:33,110
in the shop and at home.

937
00:42:33,130 --> 00:42:34,190
It was just enough.

938
00:42:34,690 --> 00:42:35,710
I couldn't wait

939
00:42:35,710 --> 00:42:37,600
to return to the burial goods store to make the deal.

940
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:38,680
But when I thought of what Dugu Yang said

941
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:40,240
about meeting at 1 o'clock,

942
00:42:41,790 --> 00:42:42,650
I was afraid that arriving too early

943
00:42:42,650 --> 00:42:44,890
would give him an excuse not to sell to me.

944
00:42:44,890 --> 00:42:46,420
So I had to endure it.

945
00:42:46,550 --> 00:42:47,910
I was about to finally get the treasure

946
00:42:47,910 --> 00:42:49,290
I've been longing for half a lifetime.

947
00:42:49,290 --> 00:42:51,340
I was so happy about it.

948
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:54,180
When the time came,

949
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:55,880
the rain had also stopped.

950
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:58,700
When I hurried to the burial goods store,

951
00:42:59,220 --> 00:43:01,020
I found that the lights were off.

952
00:43:03,830 --> 00:43:05,510
What a despicable coroner.

953
00:43:06,290 --> 00:43:07,450
How dare you fool me?

954
00:43:11,670 --> 00:43:12,900
It makes no sense.

955
00:43:28,870 --> 00:43:29,550
Dugu Yang?

956
00:43:46,270 --> 00:43:47,020
Dugu Yang?

957
00:44:03,870 --> 00:44:05,930
I didn't report it to the authorities

958
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:08,800
because I was afraid suspicion would fall on me.

959
00:44:09,680 --> 00:44:10,810
You're in court now.

960
00:44:11,030 --> 00:44:12,290
Did you tell the truth?

961
00:44:13,190 --> 00:44:15,190
Every antique in Treasure Pavilion

962
00:44:15,190 --> 00:44:16,350
is genuine.

963
00:44:16,870 --> 00:44:18,420
Every word I have said

964
00:44:19,030 --> 00:44:20,310
is true.
